5d3ba0c7aaea10539713dbee","tid":397072,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國脫歐：退歐法案二讀通過<br />\n09月12日(二) 07:37   <br />\n<br />\n英國國會下議院周二清晨投票，以326:290二讀通過「退出歐盟法案」《大廢除法案》進入下一階段。 <br />\n<br />\n英國首相文翠珊表示，脫歐法案獲進入下一階段，意味能夠在堅固的基礎上繼續進行協商。議案將在10月份進入議會委員會審核階段，接受逐行審查。 <br />\n<br />\n英國國會下議院上周四(7日)二讀辯論就脫歐問題提出的《大廢除法案》，讓英國正式離開歐盟後，立即將大部分歐盟法例過渡到英國法律管轄下，不致形成法律真空。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>留名等睇屈機Sir講英國唔會脫歐</ins></span></span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"79225b012f55beb20233759f906db91211a66351","tid":397072,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7924ff428d1344c2532488ca889074c6708e0bd","tid":397072,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1<br />\n2<br />\n3<br />\n4<br />\n5<br />\n6<br />\n7<br />\n8<br />\n9<br />\n10<br />\n11<br />\n12<br />\n13<br />\n14<br />\n15<br />\n16<br />\n17<br />\n18<br />\n19<br />\n20<br />\n21<br />\n22<br />\n23<br />\n24<br />\n25<br />\n26<br />\n27<br />\n儲夠錢買了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">以分鐘計</span></span></blockquote><br />\n威</blockquote><br />\n做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似Facebook 啲comments <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fb92aa096c1b9412bb96d71bdb3f8002820656","tid":397072,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:01:22.000Z","msg":"儲錢買樓 不了"}]}